# HSM collector conformance v1 — file sensor contract (string content path).
# Format: case|action|arg1|arg2|...
# Actions:
# create_file_sensor|path|default_file_name|extension
# add_file_value|idx|content|status|comment   (content is UTF-8; token:null content is silently ignored)
# Contract notes:
# - AddValue(string) publishes the UTF-8 bytes as a file payload (Type 6) with the sensor
#   options' default name/extension. Disk-based SendFile stays language-specific and is NOT
#   part of this portable contract.
# - File payloads are PUSH-DRIVEN: they dispatch promptly while running and are NOT gated by
#   the package collect period (the C# file queue wakes on enqueue, unlike the batched data
#   queue). There is no orchestrable "pending at stop" state for files.
# - A null content is silently ignored; values added before Start are dropped (instant
#   sensor gating).

file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|create_collector
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|create_file_sensor|contract/file/basic|report|txt
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|start
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|add_file_value|0|hello file|Ok|file-comment
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|expect_sent_count|1|5
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|expect_payload_contains|0|"Type":6,
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|expect_payload_contains|0|"Value":"hello file"
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|expect_payload_contains|0|"Name":"report"
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|expect_payload_contains|0|"Extension":"txt"
file_add_value_utf8_roundtrip|expect_payload_contains|0|"Comment":"file-comment"

file_value_before_start_is_dropped|create_collector
file_value_before_start_is_dropped|create_file_sensor|contract/file/prestart|early|log
file_value_before_start_is_dropped|add_file_value|0|too early|Ok|prestart
file_value_before_start_is_dropped|expect_sent_count|0
file_value_before_start_is_dropped|start
file_value_before_start_is_dropped|stop
file_value_before_start_is_dropped|expect_sent_count|0

file_null_value_is_ignored|create_collector
file_null_value_is_ignored|create_file_sensor|contract/file/null|nulls|txt
file_null_value_is_ignored|start
file_null_value_is_ignored|add_file_value|0|token:null|Ok|null-content
file_null_value_is_ignored|stop
file_null_value_is_ignored|expect_sent_count|0

file_dispatches_promptly_despite_collect_period|create_collector_with_limits|20000|50|60000
file_dispatches_promptly_despite_collect_period|create_file_sensor|contract/file/prompt|prompt|log
file_dispatches_promptly_despite_collect_period|start
file_dispatches_promptly_despite_collect_period|add_file_value|0|prompt file|Ok|prompt-comment
file_dispatches_promptly_despite_collect_period|expect_sent_count|1|5
file_dispatches_promptly_despite_collect_period|expect_payload_contains|0|"Value":"prompt file"
